sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as Career Copilot UI
    participant Parser as CV Parser
    participant ATS as ATS CV Engine
    participant Match as Job Matching Engine
    participant Jobs as Job Platforms
    participant CVGen as Tailored CV Generator
    participant Roadmap as Roadmap Engine
    participant Proof as Proof Store

    Note over UI,ATS: Human-in-the-loop flow. The system can suggest, but the user must review and approve.

    User->>UI: Upload CV (PDF or Word)
    UI->>Parser: Parse CV into structured sections
    Parser-->>UI: Structured CV data
    UI->>ATS: Generate ATS-friendly master CV draft
    ATS-->>UI: ATS master CV draft
    UI-->>User: Show ATS draft for review and edits
    User->>UI: Approve corrected ATS master CV

    UI->>Match: Search jobs using approved CV evidence
    Match->>Jobs: Retrieve matching JDs
    Jobs-->>Match: JDs and metadata
    Match-->>UI: Ranked jobs with fit explanations
    UI-->>User: Display matched jobs

    User->>UI: Open one selected JD
    UI->>CVGen: Generate first JD-specific CV from approved evidence only
    CVGen-->>UI: Tailored CV draft and evidence mapping
    UI-->>User: Show draft with match and gap explanations

    opt User wants another version
        User->>UI: Submit feedback on emphasis or wording
        UI->>CVGen: Regenerate CV using feedback and approved evidence
        CVGen-->>UI: Updated JD-specific CV draft
        UI-->>User: Review regenerated draft
    end

    User->>UI: Finalize tailored CV draft

    alt Skill gaps exist for this JD
        User->>UI: Click Generate Roadmap
        UI->>Roadmap: Build JD-specific learning roadmap
        Roadmap-->>UI: Roadmap with milestones
        UI-->>User: Show roadmap
        User->>UI: Mark roadmap item complete and attach proof
        UI->>Proof: Store completion evidence
        Proof-->>UI: Evidence saved
        User->>UI: Generate updated CV version
        UI->>CVGen: Create updated CV using approved evidence and proof
        CVGen-->>UI: Updated JD-specific CV version
        UI-->>User: Review updated tailored CV
    else No major gaps
        UI-->>User: Ready to export and apply
    end
